## **5. Timeline (Semester Arc: Arc 2)**
| Weeks | Focus | Primary Outputs |
|------|------|-----------------|
| 1–2 | SDK onboarding + raw-stream access (critical path) | SDK validated, first raw stream visible in Max |
| 3–4 | Stream characterization + ingest robustness | Channel inventory, latency notes, stable Max ingest |
| 5–6 | Dataset-ready capture schema + logging | Capture format, logging pipeline, sample datasets |
