## **6. Deliverables Summary (Arc 2)**
- Precedent research dossier (artists/researchers mapping biosignals to output)
- **Muse 2 SDK validated** and raw waveform access confirmed
- **Raw signal ingest into Max/MSP + Jitter** (proof patch + visualization)
- Data stream inventory (ranges, refresh, latency)
- Dataset-ready capture schema + logging pipeline (raw + derived layers)
- Replay mechanism (recorded session → streamed back into Max)
